LEXICON TA_FUT !!= @CODE@ gives flag diacritic and directs to subjunctive person suffixes
@U.verb.fut@ TA_FUT_SUF ;


LEXICON TA_FUT_SUF

+1Sg+3SgO:%>aki		   # ;
